            <p><add hand="#barker">Land. Scarcity of writing materials.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>New Years Creek</p>
<p><persName>Col - Austin</persName>   the tract of land which I wish you to reserve for
me it being my Chois is on the <placeName>south fork of this creek begining
at or near where <persName>Allcorn </persName>desires haveing his upper line run thense<pb n="1651"/>
extending up for quantity so as to include sd branch of the creek</placeName> it
being not a permanent stream without pen ink or paper it is 
necessary to be laconick</p>

<p><persName>Tacitus Clay</persName></p>
<p><date when="1827-05-31">May the 31th&#8212;1827</date>.</p>


        </div1>
